window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Do you have a dream sitting on a shelf that you're ready to bring to life? Or maybe you've begun your journey of change but feel stuck, stalled, and uncertain about what to do next. The time has come for you to create your own path—not follow the one presented to you—and you could use a powerful dose of guidance to get you there.</p> <p>This is exactly where you need to be. In <i>Pivot and Pursue It</i>, reinvention expert and author of the Audible Original <i>Mastering the Skill of Reinvention</i>, Coach Pamela Mitchell delivers 90 minutes of concrete advice on how to envision your next destination and then get there.</p> <p>To begin, Coach Pamela guides you in defining your vision of your most fulfilling life, professionally and personally. She then coaches you, step by step, through specific prompts for identifying, organizing, and prioritizing your goals. Finally, she assists you in customizing your reinvention strategy and gives you a quick tactic for accelerating your progress. By the end of this masterclass, you’ll be primed for action with a ready-to-execute plan!</p> <p>Drawing on her nearly 20 years of coaching clients through successful leaps, in <i>Pivot and Pursue It</i> Coach Pamela gives you a simple yet powerful playbook for rethinking and reinventing yourself. This masterclass leaves you inspired and with concrete action steps to take, so you can finally live the life you’ve always dreamed of with clarity and confidence. </p>"; 
